          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The relative normalization was obtained",
                "using the yield of elastically scattered Be-9 from",
                "Au-197 recorder by a monitor detector which was placed",
                "at 19-degree. Absolute normalization is obtained by",
                "normalizing the yields obtained at two or three of the",
                "most forward angles (4.5, 6 and 7.5-degree) to the",
                "theoretical cross sections obtained from optical model",
                "calculations. Normalization procedure plus the",
                "statistical counting  error, especially at backward",
                "angles is approx. 15% in the result at these angles.",
                "The inelastic scattering yields were normalized using",
                "the Be-9+Be-9 elastic cross section at 19-degree as",
                "measured by the monitor detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
